{"name":"Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook 24/7","nodes":[{"parameters":{"formTitle":"Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook 24/7","formFields":{"values":[{"fieldLabel":"Email","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Company","requiredField":false},{"fieldLabel":"Dealstage","requiredField":false}]},"options":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"a1d63510-6128-4fff-b61e-daa05c6e1a13","name":"New Contact Form Submission","webhookId":"5b7dbea1-8bd1-4e92-84c7-bc464383284b"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"e6991f65-b125-4eba-8241-d931b2ca8ec6","leftValue":"={{ $json.contactId || $json.email }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.filter","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[54,400],"id":"ba9ef863-6a3e-45c3-80c3-59bcfeb56869","name":"Keep Valid Contacts"},{"parameters":{"compare":"selectedFields","fieldsToCompare":"contactId","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.removeDuplicates","typeVersion":2,"position":[378,400],"id":"2b668ad9-0b35-4af2-be10-bd79a4c1c31c","name":"Remove Duplicate Contacts"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"query","value":"={{ $json.email }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[702,400],"id":"75b2c45a-5fb9-4dcc-9435-90a3cb628dac","name":"Enrich — Primary Provider","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"6958dc98-c8cc-4ba5-9bc2-7afc0dee5e5b","leftValue":"={{ $json.company || $json.name }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[1026,400],"id":"7fe7681b-9e0f-41ce-b13c-fe1178b151da","name":"Primary Hit?"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://fallback-enrich.example.com/v1/person","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"email","value":"={{ $json.email }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[1350,880],"id":"89e41eea-908b-4430-a3b5-5d352c543466","name":"Enrich — Fallback Provider","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[1998,400],"id":"9dabc2b9-9972-48af-9f32-c3d77bb5c2ff","name":"Merge Enrichment Paths"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Score each contact 0-100 from simple heuristics\nreturn $input.all().map(item => {\n  const j = item.json;\n  let score = 50;\n  if (j.email) score += 20;\n  if (j.company) score += 15;\n  if ((j.source || '') === 'referral') score += 15;\n  return { json: { ...j, score: Math.min(100, score) } };\n});"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[2970,400],"id":"537748d9-d7f1-4236-98ef-1784af2e93be","name":"Score Enriched Records"},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[3294,400],"id":"96e70838-bef3-48a1-8b39-9371f29f9824","name":"Upsert into HubSpot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"d96c48d4-fbee-47c8-b73c-a59c26cb8988","leftValue":"={{ $json.score >= 80 }}","rightValue":true,"operator":{"type":"boolean","operation":"true"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[3618,400],"id":"283c2f95-b04e-4a68-a12e-c1a51929338e","name":"Hot Lead?"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#sales","cachedResultName":"#sales"},"text":"=🔥 Hot {{ $json.company || $json.email }} (score {{ $json.score }}) — reach out now","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[3942,160],"id":"185c0063-9ac9-4978-a05a-ef9f3f12064b","name":"Ping Owner Immediately","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"query","value":"={{ $json.email }}"}]},"options":{"timeout":15000}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[4266,400],"id":"945efc16-3cf3-46c8-a24b-2996195f336c","name":"Enrich with Reference Data","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"alwaysOutputData":true,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"1e336f42-b795-4bc8-aafd-f5f0cca6ca30","name":"enrichedAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"bcb43086-4553-4b14-a67d-851fb49cfaed","name":"enrichmentSource","value":"reference-api","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[4590,400],"id":"d760d78b-cc76-4f9a-88ac-341826817f78","name":"Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"operation":"csv","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.convertToFile","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[4914,400],"id":"4c12babf-f200-4da7-8e9e-a215f03eadb3","name":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Contact Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[5238,400],"id":"cf112c86-f8ff-4557-9f85-ad20f1ea67fc","name":"Archive Row Snapshot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"completedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[5562,400],"id":"d240387a-d26a-4f2b-a613-085479bab9a9","name":"Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"dataToSave":{"values":[{"key":"runId","value":"={{ $execution.id }}"},{"key":"itemCount","value":"={{ $items().length }}"}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.executionData","typeVersion":1,"position":[5886,400],"id":"9425767a-5086-4b5a-8f35-ea56a157245a","name":"Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"ff97da6a-113e-4624-8207-311baf0ae2b6","name":"runAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"682c429a-5166-4cad-ad24-52fe0e5283b3","name":"itemCount","value":"={{ $input.all().length }}","type":"number"},{"id":"55951a46-eb20-4a6b-8ba0-2b69b01d20ef","name":"status","value":"completed","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[6210,400],"id":"6f7d5797-72be-4346-aee5-ca114b1f6d63","name":"Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Contact Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[6534,400],"id":"9ff90405-9b77-4cf5-ba94-4c615b77cb64","name":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#sales","cachedResultName":"#sales"},"text":"=✅ Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook 24/7 — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[6858,400],"id":"05668db9-5573-4a50-9294-f760b9ed1db0","name":"Send Summary to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"6ebefd32-348d-410c-92dc-7e2c1a85aded","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"ff7f911f-fd6c-4372-81c4-3a983a506104","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"efabd987-46ba-4a90-9db5-4cb6423fe58b","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[6210,1420],"id":"2e4d65b0-aa27-4637-a35d-255486cc0eee","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"subject":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage ","bodyContent":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","toRecipients":"={{ $json.email || 'ops@company.com' }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[6534,1420],"id":"5011011e-6353-4427-a1c6-e07676463e4f","name":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Contact Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[6858,1420],"id":"3ca81014-355c-4aab-8c35-78a630bb1cdd","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### New Contact Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (Email, Company, Dealstage). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Keep Valid Contacts","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"1eb0dd1b-3240-6a95-6977-49289b66a961","name":"Note: New Contact Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Keep Valid Contacts\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Remove Duplicate Contacts","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"e01b37ee-3729-2782-e51d-9316c94f1789","name":"Note: Keep Valid Contacts"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Remove Duplicate Contacts\n\nDrops duplicates within this run (compared on `contactId`).\n\nNext: Enrich — Primary Provider","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"771cfda6-1e28-15d8-d629-39d7c5527a44","name":"Note: Remove Duplicate Contacts"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich — Primary Provider\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Primary Hit? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"b073e765-9c37-2ed5-4a08-3d45bf566aaf","name":"Note: Enrich — Primary Provider"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Primary Hit?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.company || $json.name }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Enrichment Paths · ②→ Enrich — Fallback Provider","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"7a3eb28d-b717-4ceb-7b88-5e0bffe82189","name":"Note: Primary Hit?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich — Fallback Provider\n\nGET https://fallback-enrich.example.com/v1/person — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Enrichment Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1000],"id":"9b6214ee-0579-3691-4a66-19477caf7060","name":"Note: Enrich — Fallback Provider"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Enrichment Paths\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Score Enriched Records","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"318ae3df-201a-7cfe-2b47-0b1c7311f6e2","name":"Note: Merge Enrichment Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Score Enriched Records\n\nCustom JavaScript: Score each contact 0-100 from simple heuristics\n\nNext: Upsert into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"719296e8-da9c-0cf9-b893-1f1b07a06033","name":"Note: Score Enriched Records"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert into HubSpot\n\nCreates or updates a HubSpot contact by email — HubSpot is the CRM system of record for this pipeline.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hot Lead? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"5c2e24a5-802a-14b8-cc1c-b4e3b17bba01","name":"Note: Upsert into HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hot Lead?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.score >= 80 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Ping Owner Immediately · ②→ Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"d558b09a-ad3d-6d12-41f2-78739cc19844","name":"Note: Hot Lead?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Ping Owner Immediately\n\nSends an email via Microsoft Outlook — recipient comes from the item's `email` field.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,280],"id":"3531bfa2-d62d-e6b1-fa37-5f160bcc778b","name":"Note: Ping Owner Immediately"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"429d0682-46eb-e0fb-79d7-67adefefccea","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"b4600465-c85f-6b67-1b3a-289cc0fb024e","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"b88dda8f-5330-6a82-dccf-9f951fcd030e","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\nAppends a new row to 'Contact Tracker' — a human-readable audit trail that doesn't require opening n8n to inspect.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"ec2b4508-e424-49d1-0718-355d75c0c136","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"28be368b-9caa-55c9-48db-b32cdbf45e47","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"85da763b-887a-1a45-06b7-46740ab7cfa4","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"27c295e5-d473-f8e2-20cf-336a5dd07cde","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\nAppends a new row to 'Contact Tracker' — a human-readable audit trail that doesn't require opening n8n to inspect.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"6ca8fe1f-c4b0-b7a9-36df-90a5e333279f","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nPosts a message to Slack (`#sales`) — a low-latency way for the team to see automation activity without checking a dashboard.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"1f52c6b7-a546-78aa-cd3d-29aeb8bfd229","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Outlook","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,1540],"id":"28cf4d1e-f1eb-e9bd-6e79-325f60498b84","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Outlook\n\nSends an email via Microsoft Outlook — recipient comes from the item's `email` field.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,1540],"id":"89d0acd0-2283-46f0-b313-f58ddfd37c39","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nAppends a new row to 'Contact Tracker' — a human-readable audit trail that doesn't require opening n8n to inspect.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,1540],"id":"5a501e86-37fc-192d-12f4-9790031ba2ba","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Qualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** Lead Capture & Routing · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nQualify inbound leads with HubSpot and Outlook 24/7. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual deal updates is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Contact Form Submission → Keep Valid Contacts → Remove Duplicate Contacts → Enrich — Primary Provider → Primary Hit? → Merge Enrichment Paths → Score Enriched Records → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to lead capture & routing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating deal updates in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; HubSpot private-app token; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.\n\n## Try it now\nSample data is pinned on the trigger — hit **Execute Workflow** to watch it flow through every node before connecting any real credentials. Unpin the trigger (right-click → Unpin) when you're ready to go live.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"ce4822c3-a3cf-68d2-f2c3-0b53708785ca","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## Design decisions\n\nThe fallback enrichment provider only fires when the primary genuinely misses (checked explicitly, not assumed) — paying for two enrichment calls per lead when the first one already worked would double the cost for no benefit. Scoring runs after enrichment, not before, so the score reflects the richest data available rather than just what arrived on the original request.","width":480,"height":300,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,1020],"id":"58c34f94-b9ac-b020-7bd8-41b68a6a6a1f","name":"🎓 Design Decisions"},{"parameters":{"content":"## Practice exercises\n\nAlready production-grade — deepen your understanding:\n\n1. Force the primary provider to miss (e.g. a bad URL) and confirm the fallback picks up the slack.\n2. Add a third-provider rung to the waterfall after the fallback.\n3. Change the hot-lead threshold and watch how often the immediate-ping branch fires.","width":480,"height":340,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,1360],"id":"9a0da02c-c035-4f8b-81f9-f4fb7851877c","name":"🧪 Practice Exercises"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"9509412d-2e08-7969-8c75-885e934a76c9","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"35847c32-71ad-858a-c9bd-beda61c38b98","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your deal updates process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"87f096d0-b579-d7a6-a945-718042ab0b33","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Contact Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Keep Valid Contacts","type":